  [dialog 1/5]   |       "role": "assistant",
  [dialog 1/5]   |       "content": "Swap the Big Mac for a 20-piece chicken nuggets, and the fries for a side salad. Keep the Coke, that's all, thanks."
  [dialog 1/5]   |     },
  [dialog 1/5]   |     {
  [dialog 1/5]   |       "role": "user",
  [dialog 1/5]   |       "content": "Got it, a side salad. I can't confirm a 20-piece nugget or regular Coke right now, but we have 10-piece nuggets and Diet Coke that are safe for your lactose intolerance."
  [dialog 1/5]   |     },
  [dialog 1/5]   |     {
  [dialog 1/5]   |       "role": "assistant",
  [dialog 1/5]   |       "content": "10-piece nuggets, a side salad, and a Diet Coke. That's all, thanks."
  [dialog 1/5]   |     },
  [dialog 1/5]   |     {
  [dialog 1/5]   |       "role": "user",
  [dialog 1/5]   |       "content": "Got it, a side salad and a Diet Coke. I can't confirm the 10-piece nuggets right now, would you like to swap that for something else?"
  [dialog 1/5]   |     },
  [dialog 1/5]   |     {
  [dialog 1/5]   |       "role": "assistant",
  [dialog 1/5]   |       "content": "Swap the nuggets for a McChicken. That's all, thanks."
  [dialog 1/5]   |     },
  [dialog 1/5]   |     {
  [dialog 1/5]   |       "role": "user",
  [dialog 1/5]   |       "content": "I’m sorry, but the McChicken contains milk, so it’s not suitable for lactose intolerance. We do have a side salad and a Diet Coke, which are dairy‑free, and we can also offer regular fries if that works for you. Does that sound good?"
  [dialog 1/5]   |     }
  [dialog 1/5]   |   ],
  [dialog 1/5]   |   "response": "Yes, the fries work. That's all, thanks."
